{"Id":500370,"Title":"毗陵薛黉自号渊泉求铭其室","Dynasty":"明","Author":"管讷","Context":"五行在天，惟一生水。水之有本，源原于始。潴之斯止，孰曰匪渊。道之斯达，孰曰匪泉。盈科后进，弗停一息。维静维深，厥本乃立。弗澄则浊，罔睹山岳。弗挠则清，毫发乃明。挠之澄之，清浊辨焉。匪水若兹，惟人亦然。心而弗澄，百欲是兴。身而弗挠，一私靡扰。昔在圣贤，观厥川海。以近取譬，道无不在。允尔泓父，逝者若斯。我告尔铭，永言服之。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"3f065d55d0138f3e91cb0ed17456d60c","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6840540,"Sentence":"五行在天，惟一生水。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǔ háng zài tiān ，wéi yī shēng shui ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6840541,"Sentence":"水之有本，源原于始。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shui zhī yǒu běn ，yuán yuán yú shi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6840542,"Sentence":"潴之斯止，孰曰匪渊。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhū zhī sī zhi ，shú yuē fěi yuān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6840543,"Sentence":"道之斯达，孰曰匪泉。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"dāo zhī sī dá ，shú yuē fěi quán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6840544,"Sentence":"盈科后进，弗停一息。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yīng kē hòu jìn ，fú tǐng yī xī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6840545,"Sentence":"维静维深，厥本乃立。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wéi jìng wéi shēn ，jué běn nǎi lì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6840546,"Sentence":"弗澄则浊，罔睹山岳。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fú chéng zé zhuó ，wǎng dǔ shān yuè ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6840547,"Sentence":"弗挠则清，毫发乃明。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fú náo zé qīng ，háo fā nǎi mǐng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6840548,"Sentence":"挠之澄之，清浊辨焉。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"náo zhī chéng zhī ，qīng zhuó biàn yān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":68